{"tid":2508018,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中大二號橋案 證物標籤多處出錯 警員：只屬「差別」而非「重點」可接受","createTime":"2021-04-28T12:02:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T12:36:11.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c8ccbe58beae8ec9c1be13cc46df9c0b95f0af04","tid":2508018,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T12:02:48.000Z","msg":"辯方盤問有份接收涉案證物的偵緝警員，揭露他為證物撰寫標籤時有多處疏漏，例如沒有為標籤簽名、負責案件的隊伍名稱有出入、甚至同袍寫錯英文名仍照樣簽名作實。警員聲言查案隊伍名稱有出入只是「差別」而非「重點」，認為如此差別可以接受，又稱當時只檢查標籤有否準確描述證物狀態，以及是否寫上正確警員編號。<br />\n<br />\n偵緝警員12799李梓濱案發時隸屬沙田警區重案組第三隊，現隸屬東九龍總區反三合會行動組第二隊。他供稱前年11月12日從5名同袍手中接收涉及5名當天被捕人士共91件證物，包括本案被告，並將5人的物品分開放進5個證物袋內，放置於其辦公室桌底後，繼續調查本案。3天後，他將證物交予駐守警署證物室的同袍。<br />\n<br />\n及後大狀要求李查看第三被告部份證物的標籤，指出數項出入之處。辯方指，屬於第三被告的豬嘴，標籤上註明負責案件的隊伍一欄填上沙田警區重案組第三隊；惟眼罩的標籤則寫上由新界南總區重案組1B隊負責案件。<br />\n<br />\n李解釋謂，案件起初的確由沙田警區重案組負責，惟其後改由新界南總區重案組接手。他聲言，填寫該標籤時沒有發現這點，並謂：「呢個係一個差別，但唔係一個重點。」他又稱如此差別可以接受。<br />\n<br />\n辯方質疑李沒有為屬於第三被告手套的標籤簽名，李稱當時「簽漏咗，遺忘咗」。辯方再指，第三被告背囊的標籤將負責警員的編號寫成「10209」。李表示不認識編號10209的同袍，不知道該同袍隸屬哪一隊，亦不記得他本人有否為該背囊填寫標籤並簽名。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210428/CGTNFKBEXZBQZKMG662RLAKDGU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210428%2FCGTNFKBEXZBQZKMG662RLAKDGU%2F&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzVCKRJWvDXkpEFRbHtszOvM%3D&h=eb6b3c18\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210428%2FCGTNFKBEXZBQZKMG662RLAKDGU%2F&h=b38f222b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210428/CGTNFKBEXZBQZKMG662RLAKDGU/</a>"},{"pid":"a75e4dbaf903ba141e67733cdbfa7e6523b9fafd","tid":2508018,"uid":347130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T12:03:44.000Z","msg":"CLS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dbf9f76741e65892e318a5da304bf2ab3ee6464","tid":2508018,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T12:03:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9c1c30b50102e7e53279b750ce601ac67f6aecb","tid":2508018,"uid":50386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T12:07:20.000Z","msg":"佢老母係雞<br />\n同<br />\n佢老母食雞<br />\n都係差別唔係重點<br />\n可接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceb5605f20fba97c3a17f023e04732ba5fb19d56","tid":2508018,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T12:13:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1db98c9d5d0e3f7f24069a52110352a174c637b","tid":2508018,"uid":291990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T12:18:38.000Z","msg":"死黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33d2a1612efd179c6bd00b1f208223ac3f3e76f3","tid":2508018,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T12:33:57.000Z","msg":"on9 popo<br />\n<br />\n#SENDTROOPSTOLIBERATEHK<br />\n#HKSOS<br />\n#LetMyPeopleGo<br />\n#HKEXITBAN<br />\n#GiveHKersArms<br />\n#StandWithHongKong<br />\n#MilkTeaAlliance<br />\n#FreeHongKong<br />\n#CCP_is_terrorist<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[Twitter戰線] 煲大港共封港法案 狂推Hashtags求救<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/hbvoAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/hbvoAS</a>"},{"pid":"a04c8d6ef19b08878f87bb5bd5e67f2d6e77eef3","tid":2508018,"uid":245388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T12: